Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.84,1:19:05.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\fn方正标雅宋_GBK}翻译/时轴：Ming  压制：泠泫凝
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.23,1:19:11.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}月のない夜のように静かな
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.06,1:19:15.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}シンボルのない暗闇を
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.98,1:19:21.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}知らないふりして振りまいた
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.08,1:19:24.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1}光は生物で
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.90,1:19:30.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}取り出す時には気をつけて
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.88,1:19:35.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}痛みやすいから丁寧に
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.77,1:19:40.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}ぬくもりが欲しくてたまらないこと
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.51,1:19:44.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}誰にもバレないで
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.37,1:19:49.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}私達の誰もが
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.89,1:19:54.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}いつか永遠に眠る人々
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.76,1:19:57.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}欠けた月の光は
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.27,1:20:00.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}水面をキャンパスに描いた
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.07,1:20:04.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}鱗のような輝きを
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.58,1:20:07.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}孤独や凡庸さを欠いて
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.06,1:20:09.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&}人は大人になれない
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.82,1:20:14.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\t(600,2100,\c&H283A67&)}現実に加筆はいらない
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.33,1:20:20.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}美しさや光を見つけたいのなら
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.09,1:20:41.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}題名のない毎日
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.41,1:20:44.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}引き伸ばしの毎日
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.10,1:20:46.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}かかりつけの病院に
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.72,1:20:49.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}行くだけの毎日
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.11,1:20:54.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&}この先もう２度と会うことはない人の
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.53,1:20:59.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\t(200,1700,\c&H695028&\c&H695028&)}視線が刺さって抜けないや
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.55,1:21:23.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}ポツンと浮かぶ白い
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.07,1:21:25.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}雲のようにきままに
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.96,1:21:28.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}風に流されて
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.24,1:21:33.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}自由意志など初めから
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.18,1:21:37.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}ないのだと知って尚、歩く
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.10,1:21:41.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}足跡は消えないよ
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.38,1:21:43.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}欠けた月の光は
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.79,1:21:46.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}水面をキャンパスに描いた
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.52,1:21:50.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}鱗のような輝きを
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.17,1:21:53.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}孤独や凡庸さを欠いて
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.82,1:21:56.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}人は大人になれない
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.33,1:22:00.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}現実に加筆はいらない
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.95,1:22:07.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&}美しさや光を見つけたいのなら
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.23,1:19:11.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fax0.06}静谧如无月之夜
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.06,1:19:15.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fax0.06}面对无以名状的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.98,1:19:21.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fax0.06}我故作不知  将光芒挥洒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.08,1:19:24.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fax0.06}光芒本是鲜活之物
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.90,1:19:30.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}取出时务必多加留意
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.88,1:19:35.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}因其脆弱易损  务必轻柔待之
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.77,1:19:40.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}心底对温暖的渴求难以自抑
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.51,1:19:44.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}不愿让任何人察觉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.37,1:19:49.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}我们终有一天
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.89,1:19:54.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}都会归于永恒的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.76,1:19:57.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}残月的清辉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.27,1:20:00.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}以水面为画布
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.07,1:20:04.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}勾勒出鱼鳞般的粼粼波光
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.58,1:20:07.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}若缺少了孤独与平庸
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.06,1:20:09.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06}人便无法真正长成大人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.82,1:20:14.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H49603C&\fax0.06\t(600,2100,\c&H283A67&)}无需为现实添枝加叶
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.33,1:20:20.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}若想寻觅美好与光芒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.09,1:20:41.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}那些无名的日复一日
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.41,1:20:44.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}被无限拉长的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.10,1:20:46.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}只是往返于
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.72,1:20:49.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}常去医院的每一天
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.11,1:20:54.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06}此生再也不会相遇的某个人的视线
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.53,1:20:59.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H283A67&\fax0.06\t(200,1700,\c&H695028&\c&H695028&)}如尖刺般深深扎入  再也无法拔除
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.55,1:21:23.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}就如同孑然漂浮的白云
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.07,1:21:25.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.96,1:21:28.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}任风裹挟着漂泊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.24,1:21:33.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}从一开始就明知自由意志不存在
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.18,1:21:37.10,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}仍要继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.10,1:21:41.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}走过的足迹永远不会消失
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.38,1:21:43.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}残月的清辉
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.79,1:21:46.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}以水面为画布
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.52,1:21:50.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}勾勒出鱼鳞般的粼粼波光
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.17,1:21:53.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}若缺少了孤独与平庸
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.82,1:21:56.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}人便无法真正长成大人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.33,1:22:00.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}无需为现实添枝加叶
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.95,1:22:07.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\c&H695028&\fax0.06}若想寻觅美好与光芒
